21788124-cc55-4e2d-96b0-7c9075ec5011.title: Drezel
21788124-cc55-4e2d-96b0-7c9075ec5011.text:
Oh! You do not appear to be one of those Zamorakians
who imprisoned me! Who are you and why are you
here?

762da998-ba86-4e30-92f8-38063eba5f58.title: <player>
762da998-ba86-4e30-92f8-38063eba5f58.text:
My name's <player>. King Roald sent me to find
out what was going on at the temple. I take it you are
Drezel?

85b49f5f-5d37-4a31-a29c-1b68533da15f.title: Drezel
85b49f5f-5d37-4a31-a29c-1b68533da15f.text:
That's right! Oh, praise be to Saradomin! All is not yet
lost!

e8a26ee9-5332-4fc8-96ec-256036343720.title: Drezel
e8a26ee9-5332-4fc8-96ec-256036343720.text:
I feared that when those Zamorakians attacked this place
and imprisoned me up here, Misthalin would be doomed!

8025b3bb-64c5-4556-a4b9-e9a9fe49f5cf.title: Drezel
8025b3bb-64c5-4556-a4b9-e9a9fe49f5cf.text:
If they should manage to desecrate the holy River
Salve, we will be defenceless against the vampyres of
Morytania!

options.text: Why is the river such a good defence?

42f0b050-1719-4b1d-bdbc-a62ea2d2cd1f.title: Drezel
42f0b050-1719-4b1d-bdbc-a62ea2d2cd1f.text:
Well, let's just say if we cannot undo whatever damage
has been done here, the entire land is in grave peril!

c2cd6d0c-298d-49cd-beba-e2497860e18b.title: Drezel
c2cd6d0c-298d-49cd-beba-e2497860e18b.text:
So what do you say adventurer? Will you aid me and
all of Misthalin in foiling this Zamorakian plot?

94368fff-b549-4eeb-ad70-57fa600fcdf1.title: Drezel
94368fff-b549-4eeb-ad70-57fa600fcdf1.text:
Oooooh... I knew it was too good to be true... Then
leave me to my fate villain, there's no need to taunt me
as well as keeping me imprisoned.

8b4b4ade-fe00-45a9-b7df-bcaa045d57bf.title: <player>
8b4b4ade-fe00-45a9-b7df-bcaa045d57bf.text: Why is the river such a good defence?

8a7f43e7-14c6-40a5-9b88-baddabbaa95a.title: Drezel
8a7f43e7-14c6-40a5-9b88-baddabbaa95a.text:
I'm not sure if this is the best time for a history lesson.
I suppose I can give you a brief overview though. It
might help you understand our next steps.

4a7a304e-1e69-4a1a-8d86-ece7110b1cd7.title: Drezel
4a7a304e-1e69-4a1a-8d86-ece7110b1cd7.text:
It is said that many years ago, the land that is now
Morytania was a peaceful Saradominist kingdom. Alas,
all that ended when the vampyres invaded, claiming the
land as their own.

969554d3-2552-4305-a63a-21fcb35b779a.title: Drezel
969554d3-2552-4305-a63a-21fcb35b779a.text:
Morytania wasn't enough for them though. Soon, they
set their sights on these lands as well.

03661a49-8d54-4d6e-a0bf-d43d5b4fdda4.title: Drezel
03661a49-8d54-4d6e-a0bf-d43d5b4fdda4.text:
Misthalin would have quickly fallen to the vampyres,
were it not for the the bravery of the Seven Priestly
Warriors.

a3ba7091-f04c-4872-a756-c02417679734.title: Drezel
a3ba7091-f04c-4872-a756-c02417679734.text:
They led the armies of Misthalin against the vampyres
in a great battle that took place right where this temple
stands.

28c6489a-499d-4f3c-9f2a-930b0b00dc1d.title: Drezel
28c6489a-499d-4f3c-9f2a-930b0b00dc1d.text:
For ten days and nights they fought, never sleeping,
never eating, fuelled by their desire to make the world a
better place for humans to live.

9218f7ad-6564-4ea7-9869-c60db994b7b2.title: Drezel
9218f7ad-6564-4ea7-9869-c60db994b7b2.text:
On the eleventh day they were to be joined by
reinforcements. However, when those reinforcements
arrived, they found the Seven Priestly Warriors and
their forces had been slain by the vampyres.

1dc75e53-ee4c-4c38-abe1-b4e9a0ff7953.title: Drezel
1dc75e53-ee4c-4c38-abe1-b4e9a0ff7953.text:
Their sacrifice was not in vain though. Before they
were defeated, the Seven Priestly Warriors managed to
bless the Salve with the holy power of Saradomin.

30f80e7d-9f9a-4c8f-9f95-8b8f353ffa7a.title: Drezel
30f80e7d-9f9a-4c8f-9f95-8b8f353ffa7a.text:
Their blessings remain to this day, ensuring no
vampyre can cross the river.

0aaeb9d2-c5df-4c00-9e41-a9ce29d630db.title: Drezel
0aaeb9d2-c5df-4c00-9e41-a9ce29d630db.text:
The temple here was built soon after. It guards the
source of the River Salve, and acts as the only passage
between Misthalin and Morytania.

3ac73387-0b1a-4d9e-b628-f47d8b846c39.title: Drezel
3ac73387-0b1a-4d9e-b628-f47d8b846c39.text:
Once the temple was complete, the bodies of the Seven
Priestly Warriors were laid to rest in tombs of honour
in the mausoleum below. On the top of each tomb, a
golden gift was placed as a mark of respect.

71634f6b-dfec-4315-9327-2e2912d67210.title: Drezel
71634f6b-dfec-4315-9327-2e2912d67210.text:
A great statue was also built over the river, so that all
who might try and cross into Misthalin would know that
these lands are protected by Saradomin himself.

16241dc0-8579-48dd-97f4-e3168bb9fad6.title: <player>
16241dc0-8579-48dd-97f4-e3168bb9fad6.text:
Okay, I can see how the river protects the border.
Where do these Zamorakians fit in though?

b93da591-8841-4359-a09e-48561a609e31.title: Drezel
b93da591-8841-4359-a09e-48561a609e31.text:
Well, as much as it saddens me to say so adventurer,
Lord Saradomin's presence has not been felt on the
land for many years now.

0b60ee60-9804-4baf-ac26-dbda69554dda.title: Drezel
0b60ee60-9804-4baf-ac26-dbda69554dda.text:
Of course, while we know that he still watches over us,
his power here is not as strong as it once was.

d3d7ef50-fbb9-4998-b3ea-9ab72d8bf98a.title: Drezel
d3d7ef50-fbb9-4998-b3ea-9ab72d8bf98a.text:
I fear this group of Zamorakians intends to take
advantage of that. If they can somehow pollute the
Salve, the blessings on the river might fail.

98456e3c-1d5c-4365-b7b6-9730d8d0438f.title: Drezel
98456e3c-1d5c-4365-b7b6-9730d8d0438f.text:
If that happens, there won't be anything to stop an
invasion from Morytania.

7f5ec2dc-8cbc-44ea-bd4b-ae50cde221a1.title: Drezel
7f5ec2dc-8cbc-44ea-bd4b-ae50cde221a1.text:
So what do you say adventurer? Will you aid me and
all of Misthalin in foiling this Zamorakian plot?

178e505e-8238-40cf-b742-c3e2cde57174.title: Drezel
178e505e-8238-40cf-b742-c3e2cde57174.text:
Thank you, adventurer. There is a well in the
mausoleum beneath the temple that provides direct
access to the source of the Salve. That will be where the
Zamorakians will attempt their sabotage.

87007134-9d9a-40e2-a6b1-68cbd55d7927.title: Drezel
87007134-9d9a-40e2-a6b1-68cbd55d7927.text:
We need to get to that well. However, the immediate
problem is that I'm trapped in this cell.

0cd738ed-b8ba-4455-a228-39dcce8d118a.title: Drezel
0cd738ed-b8ba-4455-a228-39dcce8d118a.text:
The key must be somewhere nearby. One of the
Zamorakians might have it, or they might have hidden it
somewhere. That's not the only problem though.

c88238cb-e9a8-4524-9ce3-cdad30df832d.title: Drezel
c88238cb-e9a8-4524-9ce3-cdad30df832d.text:
When the Salve was blessed, a small number of
vampyres were left trapped on this side of it. They
were heavily weakened, but still posed a dangerous
threat.

8be9cfdb-93fb-45e8-a628-f192f11abde0.title: Drezel
8be9cfdb-93fb-45e8-a628-f192f11abde0.text:
This coffin here contains one of those vampyres. The
Zamorakians somehow found it and brought it here with
them.

4fa9620f-c8ae-4b00-88d7-6209a56abfd1.title: <player>
4fa9620f-c8ae-4b00-88d7-6209a56abfd1.text:
I see. It doesn't seem to be posing a threat right now
though.

59d97455-3dd5-43aa-ac8e-42d15c093152.title: Drezel
59d97455-3dd5-43aa-ac8e-42d15c093152.text:
No, but as those fiendish Zamorakians pointed out to
me with delight, as I am the descendant of one of the
Seven Priestly Warriors who blessed the river, it will
likely recognise the smell of my blood.

42f2389e-c199-49af-b7bd-036b98a4dfaa.title: Drezel
42f2389e-c199-49af-b7bd-036b98a4dfaa.text:
If I get too close, it will probably wake up and kill me,
very slowly and painfully.

bfb52a66-8ac4-40ef-8959-2f0a5bd1798e.title: <player>
bfb52a66-8ac4-40ef-8959-2f0a5bd1798e.text: Maybe I could kill it somehow?

7f083090-f279-4a97-892f-2b5e8ea16782.title: Drezel
7f083090-f279-4a97-892f-2b5e8ea16782.text:
No adventurer, you should not risk waking it. Even
now, it could pose a huge threat.

69417e5f-c75a-43cb-9e24-50f2251b5461.title: Drezel
69417e5f-c75a-43cb-9e24-50f2251b5461.text:
The priests of old would incapacitate trapped vampyres
with the blessings of Saradomin. I suggest you do the
same.

d9bd7678-6db1-49d2-8558-dc07de6ace49.title: <player>
d9bd7678-6db1-49d2-8558-dc07de6ace49.text:
Right. So, I need to find the key to your cell and do
something about the vampyre. Got it.

113527aa-cf06-4df5-98ad-b7df92a05114.title: Drezel
113527aa-cf06-4df5-98ad-b7df92a05114.text:
How goes it adventurer? Any luck in finding the key to
the cell or a way of stopping the vampyre yet?

f6422f27-6b4d-4b9e-8adb-0608528e2518.title: Drezel
f6422f27-6b4d-4b9e-8adb-0608528e2518.text:
Well don't give up adventurer! That key must be
around here somewhere! I know none of those
Zamorakians ever got very far from this building!

e054ae36-5b84-43b3-a77c-262488d95abb.title: Drezel
e054ae36-5b84-43b3-a77c-262488d95abb.text:
I could hear them laughing about some gullible fool that
they tricked into killing the guard dog at the
monument.

258706a5-7575-410d-8266-601a4d522779.title: Drezel
258706a5-7575-410d-8266-601a4d522779.text:
Honestly, what kind of idiot would go around killing
things just because a stranger told them to? What kind
of oafish, numb-skulled, dim-witted...

945d3b94-505f-4290-b158-a103b9dd797f.title: <player>
945d3b94-505f-4290-b158-a103b9dd797f.text: Okay, okay, I get the picture!

options.text: Could you tell me more about this temple?

cfadf45c-9ce3-488d-b195-30cae2cfa4f8.title: <player>
cfadf45c-9ce3-488d-b195-30cae2cfa4f8.text: Could you tell me more about this temple?

563d297b-d8e2-42f6-9c8a-2a1cc1be38b3.title: Drezel
563d297b-d8e2-42f6-9c8a-2a1cc1be38b3.text:
It is said that many years ago, the land that is now
Morytania was a peaceful Saradominist kingdom. Alas,
all that ended when the vampyres invaded, claiming the
land as their own.

b2ec6284-b15b-4432-ad3a-512260cb9d5d.title: Drezel
b2ec6284-b15b-4432-ad3a-512260cb9d5d.text:
Morytania wasn't enough for them though. Soon, they
set their sights on these lands as well.

7250870d-69f3-43ae-9378-e0f46e3ec3a6.title: Drezel
7250870d-69f3-43ae-9378-e0f46e3ec3a6.text:
Misthalin would have quickly fallen to the vampyres,
were it not for the the bravery of the Seven Priestly
Warriors.

40f365ca-26c7-4b85-8132-56bffd456922.title: Drezel
40f365ca-26c7-4b85-8132-56bffd456922.text:
They led the armies of Misthalin against the vampyres
in a great battle that took place right where this temple
stands.

ba4e60ea-b2fa-4c9c-b121-a54f0e9da1d5.title: Drezel
ba4e60ea-b2fa-4c9c-b121-a54f0e9da1d5.text:
For ten days and nights they fought, never sleeping,
never eating, fuelled by their desire to make the world a
better place for humans to live.

3863073f-9c61-46a7-a1de-a3d5bc935322.title: Drezel
3863073f-9c61-46a7-a1de-a3d5bc935322.text:
On the eleventh day they were to be joined by
reinforcements. However, when those reinforcements
arrived, they found the Seven Priestly Warriors and
their forces had been slain by the vampyres.

c4edf743-dbde-46b5-a8b6-e3e1402e37fc.title: Drezel
c4edf743-dbde-46b5-a8b6-e3e1402e37fc.text:
Their sacrifice was not in vain though. Before they
were defeated, the Seven Priestly Warriors managed to
bless the Salve with the holy power of Saradomin.

7cbfdcb7-1497-4adf-bac4-f74621e0662e.title: Drezel
7cbfdcb7-1497-4adf-bac4-f74621e0662e.text:
Their blessings remain to this day, ensuring no
vampyre can cross the river.

d7951fd1-33b5-46a5-b55e-2e9c81b85e9b.title: Drezel
d7951fd1-33b5-46a5-b55e-2e9c81b85e9b.text:
The temple here was built soon after. It guards the
source of the River Salve, and acts as the only passage
between Misthalin and Morytania.

3b142bc9-dd3a-46ae-a688-a07357ac5e46.title: Drezel
3b142bc9-dd3a-46ae-a688-a07357ac5e46.text:
Once the temple was complete, the bodies of the Seven
Priestly Warriors were laid to rest in tombs of honour
in the mausoleum below. On the top of each tomb, a
golden gift was placed as a mark of respect.

0998c5ad-5454-488b-89dc-40762f8071f5.title: Drezel
0998c5ad-5454-488b-89dc-40762f8071f5.text:
A great statue was also built over the river, so that all
who might try and cross into Misthalin would know that
these lands are protected by Saradomin himself.

fc2e13b5-0331-4bda-a93a-ff248e73ae7a.title: <player>
fc2e13b5-0331-4bda-a93a-ff248e73ae7a.text: Thank you for the information. I'll get going.

00b9f01d-4f9a-4bce-bf2b-4ab30e85b907.title: Drezel
00b9f01d-4f9a-4bce-bf2b-4ab30e85b907.text:
How goes it adventurer? Any luck in finding the key to
the cell or a way of stopping the vampyre yet?

e4329291-aac1-45db-8396-c73cbd5354f3.title: <player>
e4329291-aac1-45db-8396-c73cbd5354f3.text:
I have this key I took from one of those Zamorakian
monks!

71341663-4702-4a55-8382-3096a5146807.title: Drezel
71341663-4702-4a55-8382-3096a5146807.text:
Excellent work adventurer! Quickly, try it on the door,
and see if it will free me!

e3f2e999-83a9-44b9-9047-59cfe7f934f8.title: <player>
e3f2e999-83a9-44b9-9047-59cfe7f934f8.text: The key fit the lock! You're free to leave now!

4ada58f7-1764-4b0e-ac73-5dc03c58a0dc.title: Drezel
4ada58f7-1764-4b0e-ac73-5dc03c58a0dc.text:
Excellent work, adventurer! Unfortunately, as you
know, I cannot risk waking the vampyre in that coffin.

5f7d261e-e7f2-4202-97c3-41b2cb5bf61f.title: <player>
5f7d261e-e7f2-4202-97c3-41b2cb5bf61f.text: Do you have any ideas about dealing with the vampyre?

200040ef-4aad-476d-a3a6-8bec738026f0.title: Drezel
200040ef-4aad-476d-a3a6-8bec738026f0.text:
Well, the water of the Salve should still have enough
power to work against the vampyre, even if the
Zamorakians have desecrated it.

cbdcdede-223e-4ef9-9245-121062871085.title: Drezel
cbdcdede-223e-4ef9-9245-121062871085.text: Maybe you should try and get hold of some?

43997e1d-391b-45f3-97fd-aa211e562df8.title: <player>
43997e1d-391b-45f3-97fd-aa211e562df8.text: The key fit the lock! You're free to leave now!

1cd99ac7-6b03-4a53-82df-6b8f0fa410e3.title: Drezel
1cd99ac7-6b03-4a53-82df-6b8f0fa410e3.text:
Excellent work, adventurer! Unfortunately, as you
know, I cannot risk waking the vampyre in that coffin.

fe7e0193-1553-4365-88f2-287f0db3c3b4.title: <player>
fe7e0193-1553-4365-88f2-287f0db3c3b4.text:
I have some water from the Salve. It seems to have
been desecrated though. Do you think you could bless
it for me?

8dcb8ace-2c22-4da1-91d9-fa39545ecd1f.title: Drezel
8dcb8ace-2c22-4da1-91d9-fa39545ecd1f.text:
Yes, good thinking adventurer! Give it to me, I will bless
it!

0fd03da5-3021-42d1-9d65-fd466799503e.text: Drezel blesses the water for you.

191319e0-071a-4903-9c68-7a5abaa1bb66.title: <player>
191319e0-071a-4903-9c68-7a5abaa1bb66.text:
I poured the blessed water over the coffin. I think that
should trap the vampyre in there long enough for you
to escape.

a036eb58-7895-4b2f-b624-4c8f353f1146.title: Drezel
a036eb58-7895-4b2f-b624-4c8f353f1146.text:
Excellent work adventurer! I am free at last! Let me
ensure that evil vampyre is trapped for good. I will then
meet you down in the mausoleum.

b08ad548-02f6-459a-9ad8-69c568cd628f.text: You use the key to unlock the cell door.

b4c8b85e-1762-4be2-a7d4-e33b05a48ac9.title: Drezel
b4c8b85e-1762-4be2-a7d4-e33b05a48ac9.text: Oh! Thank you! You have found the key!
